#Configuring Git pulgin on Jenkins

#Install Git on Jenkins server
sudo apt-get install -y git

#Install Github plugin on jenkins UI
Manage Jenkins > Jenkins Plugins > available > github

#Configure Git on jenkins GUI
Manage Jenkins > Global Tool Configuration > git
  

#Configuring Maven pulgin on Jenkins

Install Maven on Jenkins

Download maven packages https://maven.apache.org/download.cgi onto Jenkins server. Usinf  /opt/maven as my installation directory

https://dlcdn.apache.org/maven/maven-3/3.8.5/binaries/apache-maven-3.8.5-bin.tar.gz
